overview: No matter how hard you try, you can't take the trailer park outta the girl...but why would you even wanna try? Let these beauties go round the outside and show you a heck of a good time in legendary director Axel Braun's latest flick, featuring a powerhouse anal performance by bewitching newcomer Lydia Black!  Nominated - Gonzo Movie Of The Year, XBIZ 2022
tagline: Nominated - Gonzo Movie Of The Year, XBIZ 2022
title: Trailer Park Girls
